descriptionHtml:
[color=#00ff00][size=6]                                                  Liriel [/size][/color]                                                                                                                        
[color=#00ff00][size=4]Players home.[/size][/color]                  

To get to [color=#00ff00]Liriel[/color] open map see pics for location then teleport there. 

To get a good idea of [color=#00ff00]Liriel[/color] look through the pics.   
[color=#00ff00]Liriel[/color] has mannequins, weapon racks, soil for planting, tanning rack forge. 

I have tested the navmesh with a follower and encountered no problems.

[color=#00ff00][size=5]Requirements:[/size][/color]          Dawnguard.Hearthfire.Dragonborn.

[color=#00ff00][size=5]Installation:[/size][/color]          Just download with Nexus mod manger, Mod organiser or manual,if you want to install it manually,                                                                                              then you have to extract it into your data file for Skyrim.

[color=#00ff00][size=5]Unistallation:[/size][/color]         Just untick in mod manger or mod organiser or delete the files you manually installed.
